member.name: T:FSharpx.Collections.Experimental.SkewBinomialHeap`1
member.summary: A SkewBinomialHeap is a priority queue where elements are inserted in any order, using "insert" and are extracted in either ascending or descending order using "head", "peek", "tail", "pop" or any of their "try" variants.
